text: Actually, i ate a teriyaki glazed chiken rice. And its good enough also. If you reached at the end of the botanic garden, do not going back to the starts, visit here and be fill your hunger..
The current place is much cleaner than previous food court.  But the food is so much better before than the current one.
The chicken rice is so delicious and the chicken is tender. Expect queue about 15 minutes

Not sure whether opened by Eric teo but his photo is there. Should ask him try the chicken rice to see whether he can bite and swallow the rubbery chicken. If you have nothing to eat go for it. My threshold is already very high for those following me. To get a 3* from me means a lot will be giving 1-2*
